label: Kralji Ulice
title: Kralji_Ulice
exrest: Kralji ulice is a Slovenian monthly street newspaper specialized on homelessness and related social issues. It is offered on the streets of Ljubljana and other Slovenian cities, mostly by the homeless, people at risk of homelessness and other people in social or economic distress. The goal of the newspaper is to offer them the opportunity to earn a legitimate income, thereby helping them to reintegrate into mainstream society. The newspaper is in part created by the very same people that offer it on the streets. It contains life stories, anecdotes, reflections, pictorial material, poems, professional articles, reports and other materials that illuminate homelessness in Slovenia from different angles.
